<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#008000">(أ)</span> مِنْ هَدْيِهِ التَّطَوُّعِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#008000">(ب)</span> وَمِنْ أُضْحِيَّتِهِ وَلَوْ وَاجِبَةً.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#008000">(ج)</span> وَيَجُوزُ مِنَ المُتْعَةِ وَالقِرَانِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- وَيَجِبُ أَنْ يَتَصَدَّقَ بِمَا يَقَعُ عَلَيْهِ اسْمُ اللَّحْمِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَيُعْتَبَرُ تَمْلِيكُ الفَقِيرِ، فَلَا يَكْفِي إِطْعَامُهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَإِذَا دَخَلَ العَشْرُ حَرُمَ عَلَى مَنْ يُضَحِّي أَوْ يُضَحَّى عَنْهُ أَخْذُ شَيْءٍ مِنْ شَعْرِهِ أَوْ ظُفُرِهِ أَوْ بَشَرَتِهِ إِلَى الذَّبْحِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَسُنَّ حَلْقٌ بَعْدَهُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَالعَقِيقَةُ سُنَّةٌ مُؤَكَّدَةٌ فِي حَقِّ الأَبِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهِيَ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- عَنِ الغُلَامِ شَاتَانِ مُتَقَارِبَتَانِ سِنًّا وَشَبَهًا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فَإِنْ عَدِمَ فَوَاحِدَةٌ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَعَنِ الجَارِيَةِ شَاةٌ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- وَلَا يُجْزِئُ بَدَنةٌ أَوْ بَقَرَةٌ إِلَّا كَامِلَةً.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>